dct_title_s: General highway and transportation map, Kosciusko County, Indiana
dct_description_sm: State roads revised to January 1, 1949.; 1937.; Data obtained from State-wide Highway Planning Survey.; Includes location map and chart of Culture in unincorporated places.; Supplementary sheet includes maps of Lake Wawasee, Tippecanoe Lake, Webster Lake, and a group of Bantam Lake, Irish Lake, Mable Lake, Plew Lake, Kuhn Lake, Barbee lake, Hammon Lake, and Heron Lake.; 49, 49A (supplementary sheet). Scale 1:130,000. not 1 inch =1 mile; Polyconic projection
